{
  "stem": "13471.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- I would-- a lot of people would come visit me and take a day to look at the trials.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And over and over again, I got this reaction.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If I just had a chance to get that guy up to the house for a beer some night, I'd love to hear him talk.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But of course, it was out of the question.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But anyway-- and then he was a lecher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was one Russian-- excuse me, French court reporter who had a very generous bustal development.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she would wander into court, [LAUGHS] things waving, and Goering-- nnnnn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was the side of the courtroom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They changed every half hour, these court reporters, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And to see her come and go and Goering-- nnnnn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was just devouring her with his eyes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Goering was, as I say, a smart man, and he very quickly realized that he was dealing with someone who didn't know the tricks of the trade of cross examination.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as a result, he led Jackson down blind alleys and made him look ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was really a rather shameful, sad procedure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jackson himself realized this, but only after the end of a long day of Goering's demonstration that he was superior to Jackson.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had Jackson on the run.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so Jackson called in Sir David Maxwell Fife.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The British prosecutor.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But whose life had been in the British courts and who knew exactly how to handle a recalcitrant witness.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And within an hour of the next morning, Sir David had Goering whining and cringing, which is what Jackson just couldn't quite do.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there were quite a number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Drex Sprecher was one, although he's one of the minor ones.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dodd's-- Christopher Dodd's father was one.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
